div.p: Patriot Thanks is a web application and phone app, that is designed to assist "active duty, veterans, first responders, and their spouses," locate local area businesses that offer discounts and/or incentives to patronize their businesses. It is hoped, that local area businesses will also use this app to help increase business by showing their support for and to "active duty, veterans, first responders, and their spouses."
